AIM Office Tower is a 7-floor project that is being carried out along General Ogomudia Road, in Lekki Phase 1, Lagos, Nigeria. The project is developed by AIM Group, a multi-disciplinary company with interests in construction, project consultancy, broadcasting, and technology with the support of the group’s subsidiaries/members. Upon completion on an undisclosed date, the AIM Office Tower will serve as the broadcasting headquarters for the AIM Group which currently occupies space in AIM Plaza on Etim-Iyang Crescent, Victoria Island with the other companies in its portfolio such as CoolFM, Cool Link, Wazobia, Chocolat Royale and others. Also Read: The Waves Towers Lagos, Nigeria 